title: Online Leasing! Virtual Tours Available. One Bed One Bath Top Floor!

posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 21', 'OR Text', '21', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 825-855 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'We are centrally located in Renton, just one minute from Highway 167, three minutes from I-405, and five minutes from I-5.', "Borgata's location is on a quiet street combines the safety and security of a neighborhood with the ease of apartment living.", "Our comfortable townhomes and flats are clustered along a leafy cul-de-sac on a hillside above Renton, with views of the city's twinkling lights below.", 'Our spacious 1, 2 and 3-bedroom apartments and townhomes feature nine-foot ceilings and oversized windows, patios, decks and gas fireplaces.', 'Make an appointment to visit Borgata Apartments and Townhomes in Renton today - our staff will welcome you, and our community will charm you!', 'Features:', 'Wheel Chair Access, Individual Climate Control, Garbage Disposal, Window Coverings, Additional Storage Units, In Unit Washer & Dryer, Large Closets, Full-Size Refrigerator, Cable Ready, Dishwasher, Microwave, Gas Fireplace, Private Balcony or Patio', 'Community Amenities:', 'Business Center, Close to Public Transportation, Reserved Covered Parking and Attached Garages*, Package Receiving, Friendly, Responsive On-Site Management Staff, Outdoor Swimming Pool and Spa, Storage Space, On-Site Maintenance Available, Attached Garage*, Community Events, Fitness Center, Security Patrol, Clubhouse', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets - Max 2 allowed, One time Fee $300, Deposit $200', 'Cat Rent $35/mnth', 'Dog Rent $50/mnth', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'd4uWAMDNg']
